e Zmey Gorynych in particular {{wp|Dobrynya Nikitich#Dobrynya and the Dragon|shown to be deceptive}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nHydreigon may be a combination of \'\'{{wp|Lernaean Hydra|hydra}}\'\', \'\'drei\'\' (German for \'\'three\'\'), and \'\'dragon\'\'. It may also incorporate {{wp|hydrogen}}, a gas highly flammable under normal conditions.\n\nSazandora may be a combination of 三 \'\'san\'\' (three) and \'\'dragon\'\' or \'\'hydra\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=dark|type2=dragon\n|ja=サザンドラ \'\'Sazandora\'\'|jameaning=\'\'Sa\'\' and \'\'zan\'\' are from {{tt|三 \'\'sa\'\'/\'\'san\'\'|three}}, \'\'dora\'\' is from \'\'dragon\'\' or \'\'hydra\'\'\n|fr=Trioxhydre|frmeaning=From \'\'trio\'\' and {{wp|Lernaean Hydra|{{tt|\'\'Hydre\'\'|Hydra}}}}\n|es=Hydreigon|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Trikephalo|demeaning=From \'\'tri\'\' and \'\'{{tt|kephalos|Greek for head}}\'\'\n|it=Hydreigon|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=삼삼드래 \'\'Samsamdrae\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|삼/三 \'\'sam\'\'|three}} and \'\'dragon\'\'\n|zh_cmn=三頭龍 / 三头龙 \'\'Sāntóulóng\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Literally "Three-headed dragon"\n|ru=Хайдрайгон \'\'Khaydraygon\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Hydreigon (Gates to Infinity)]]\n* [[Pseudo-legendary Pokémon]]\n\n==Notes==\n<references />\n\n==External links==\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Dark|type2=Dragon}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Dark|prevnum=634|prev=Zweilous|nextnum=636|next=Larvesta}}\n|}\n{{-}}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Trikephalo]]\n[[es:Hydreigon]]\n[[fr:Trioxhydre]]\n[[it:Hydreigon]]\n[[ja:サザンドラ]]\n[[zh:三首恶龙]]'}